    "title": "Kumshinda Shetani",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "kumshinda shetani",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Waandishi wa Agano Jipya waliamini katika uhalisia wa uovu na hatari za ulimwengu wa kiroho. Walimwona Shetani, anayejulikana pia kama &quot;mwovu&quot; au &quot;ibilisi,&quot; kama tishio kubwa. Ibilisi huzuia kazi ya watu wa Mungu (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:18\">1 Wathesalonike 2:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:10\">Ufunuo 2:10</a>). Yeye &quot;huzunguka kama simba angurumaye, akitafuta mtu wa kummeza&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:8\">1 Petro 5:8</a>).</p><p>Dunia yote isiyomwamini Kristo iko chini ya nguvu za dhambi na shetani (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:2\">Waefeso 2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:19\">1 Yohana 5:19</a>). Paulo anamwita shetani &quot;mungu wa enzi hii ambaye amepofusha akili za wasioamini&quot; (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:4\">2 Wakorintho 4:4</a>; linganisha <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:19\">Mathayo 13:19</a>). Shetani anampinga Mungu na anajaribu kuharibu watu wake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:12\">Ufunuo 12:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:17\">17</a>). Hata hivyo, Yesu alikuja kuharibu &quot;kazi za shetani&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:8\">1 Yohana 3:8</a>).</p><p>Mungu hubadilisha kuwa jema kile ambacho shetani anakusudia kwa uovu. Kwa kufuata wazo hili, mtume Paulo anawaambia kanisa la Korintho kumwondoa mtu kutoka kwa Jamii ya Wakristo. Kwa njia hii, kwa kukutana na nguvu ya uharibifu ya shetani, mtu huyo anaweza kutubu na kupata wokovu (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor5:5\">1 Wakorintho 5:5</a>).</p><p>Wakristo wanapaswa kujisalimisha kwa Mungu na kumpinga shetani (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:7\">Yakobo 4:7</a>). Wanapaswa kuomba msaada kutoka kwa Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:13\">Mathayo 6:13</a>). Wanapaswa kutumia silaha za kiroho ambazo Mungu anatoa kwa ajili ya ulinzi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:10-Eph6:20\">Waefeso 6:10–20</a>). Wale wanaomtii Shetani wanakumbana na matokeo (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:1-Acts5:5\">Matendo 5:1–5</a>). Wakristo watiifu wako salama kwa sababu wanajua kifo cha Kristo msalabani kimekomesha nguvu za shetani (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:38-Rom8:39\">Warumi 8:38–39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:24\">1 Wakorintho 15:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:13\">Wakolosai 1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:10\">2:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:15\">15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:22\">1 Petro 3:22</a>).</p><p>Bwana huwalinda (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:18\">1 Yohana 5:18</a>). Pia wanajua kwamba Roho Mtakatifu ambaye ako ndani yao ana nguvu zaidi kuliko shetani (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:4\">1 Yohana 4:4</a>). Kupitia neno la Mungu, wanaweza kumshinda yule mwovu (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:14\">1 Yohana 2:14</a>; linganisha <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:11\">Ufunuo 12:11</a>).</p><p>Wakristo wanapaswa kuwa waangalifu dhidi ya shetani na kujilinda dhidi ya ushawishi wake. Hata hivyo, hawapaswi kuishi kwa hofu. Nguvu za Mungu ni kubwa zaidi kuliko za shetani. Hatimaye, Mungu atamshinda shetani kabisa (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:7-Rev20:10\">Ufunuo 20:7–10</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:13\">Mathayo 6:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:19\">13:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:3-Acts5:5\">Matendo 5:3–5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:38-Rom8:39\">Warumi 8:38–39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor5:5\">1 Wakorintho 5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:24\">15:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:4\">2 Wakorintho 4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:2\">Waefeso 2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:27\">4:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:10-Eph6:20\">6:10–20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:13\">Wakolosai 1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:10\">2:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:15\">15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:18\">1 Wathesalonike 2:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:7\">Yakobo 4:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:22\">1 Petro 3:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:8\">5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:14\">1 Yohana 2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:8\">3:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:4\">4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:18-1John5:19\">5:18–19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:10\">Ufunuo 2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:7-Rev12:9\">12:7–9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:11-Rev12:12\">11–12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:17\">17</a></p>",
